Text: Finally some English Audio books! Thanks a lot! I really appreciate it.
You're welcome! I've recently discovered audiobooks and am now seldom seen not wearing my head phones listening to one. Happy to share :)

Good quality for most of the book, but the last track seemed to skip. I downloaded this torrent and put it on my blackberry to play. I did not burn to cds. The quality of the last track is crappy, but you can still tell what the reader is saying.
Thanks a lot!!! Nothing better than a great Dean Koontz audiobook on cold winter evenings.
